ORMLite JDBC 4.48 API

This package provides the JDBC support for a lightweight Object Relational Mapping between Java classes and SQL databases.

See:
          Description

Packages
com.j256.ormlite.db Classes to support the JDBC database types.
com.j256.ormlite.jdbc JDBC database connection and results classes.
com.j256.ormlite.logger  
com.j256.ormlite.spring Utility classes to support Spring configurations.

 

This package provides the JDBC support for a lightweight Object Relational Mapping between Java classes and SQL databases. See the ORMLite home page for more information.
